<h1>Authentication</h1>

<p>There are two ways to authenticate through HeiaHeia API v3.</p>

<h3>OAuth2 Token (sent in a header)</h3>

<div class="snippet">
  <pre>
<code class="ruby">$ curl -H "Authorization: Bearer OAUTH-TOKEN" https://api.heiaheia.com/api/v2</code></pre>
</div>
<br/>

<h3>OAuth2 Token (sent as a parameter)</h3>

<div class="snippet">
  <pre>
<code class="ruby">$ curl https://api.heiaheia.com/api/v2/?access_token=OAUTH-TOKEN</code></pre>
</div>
<br/>

<p>Read <a href="http://oauth.net/2/" target="_blank">more about OAuth2</a>.</p>
